              👤
            </div>
            <h2 style={{ margin: 0, color: 'white', fontSize: '1.8rem' }}>{studentName}</h2>
            <div style={{ color: '#888', fontSize: '0.9rem', marginTop: '4px' }}>Toki Pona Student</div>
          </div>

          <div style={{ marginBottom: '24px' }}>
            <label style={{ display: 'block', fontSize: '0.65rem', fontWeight: 800, color: '#666', textTransform: 'uppercase', letterSpacing: '0.1em', marginBottom: '8px' }}>
              What should jan Lina know about you?
